  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt data-catalog-idref="tts_prompt">
        <p>A sailor fighting to keep his boat from going under is an example of —</p>
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="A">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_A">
          <p>internal conflict</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_A" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_A">
              <p>Internal conflict happens inside one head — fear, pride, doubt. This sailor's fight isn't in his head; look where the struggle is actually taking place.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="B">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_B">
          <p>external conflict</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_B" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-correct" data-catalog-idref="feedback_B">
              <p>Correct! The sailor is struggling against something out in the world — the storm and the sea — so the conflict is external, like the figure braced against the storm in the video.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="C">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_C">
          <p>no conflict at all</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_C" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_C">
              <p>A sailor versus a sinking boat is a life-or-death struggle — without a problem like this, you'd just have a list of stuff that happened.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice fixed="true" identifier="D">
        <div data-catalog-idref="tts_choice_D">
          <p>the resolution</p>
        </div>
        <qti-feedback-block identifier="feedback_D" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
          <qti-content-body>
            <div class="tb-feedback-incorrect" data-catalog-idref="feedback_D">
              <p>The resolution is a stage of the plot — the settling at the end. This question asks what kind of struggle the sailor is in, and nothing here is settling.</p>
            </div>
          </qti-content-body>
        </qti-feedback-block>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
